               <p>I am in partnership with Mr. Pugh. There is a piece of linen found, which I suppose was stolen ought of our warehouse; we did not miss it; it is impossible we should, we have so many hundred pieces. I have seen two of the prisoners about our warehouse several times; I can only speak to the property.</p>
               <p>
            
